latestIgtvVideos.caption:
We are thrilled to unveil the brand new website for SUMM! 

The new SUMM! branding was inspired by the art of Chinese paper cutting, dating back to the 6th century, and represents Chinese heritage as it relates to food, love, family, good blessings and fortune. 

The new website - SUMMFOODS.com - features “Where to Buy” functionality, allowing you to identify brick and mortar locations where you can purchase SUMM! products, as well as where to “Buy it Now” through stores offering online shopping. 

Head over to the new SUMMFOODS.com, at the link in bio.
